[03:04] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'have to do too much here with our prompt. We can just keep it very simple. Um, without a lot of fine-tuning, without a lot of descriptive language because we have the style applied, we\'ll get a really reliable result. So, here\'s'

[03:17] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'a really cool, you see this kind of like filmic um, cinematic motion blur in the background here. So, that\'s just the motion blur style. And then, of course, from here, we can do anything else we would normally do in Flora. So, we have'

[03:30] [scene:talk]
