[03:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'point of much more fine-tuned control. So we see like that. Um so now I can show you what it\'s like to train your own style. So there are a couple different ways to train a style'

[03:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'in Flora. Um, one of which is to actually use pre-generated content or generated content inside of Flora to make a new style. So, in this instance, I can go to um image. Let\'s say we\'ll use the sample'

